'''Abaalmarinta Filmfare''' waa abaal-marin oo lagu sharfayo fanka iyo farsamada heer sare ee [[Bollywood|aflaanta]] [[Hindiya]]. Abaalmarinta Filmfare waa mid kamid ah dhacdooyinka aflaamta ugu caansan India.<ref name="Mishra 9">Al{{citation|first=Vijay|last=Mishra|title=Bollywood Cinema: A Critical Genealogy|page=9|publisher=[[Victoria University of Wellington]]|url=http://www.victoria.ac.nz/slc/asi/publications/17-bollywood.pdf|access-date=2011-02-24}}</ref><ref name="Mehta 2005 135–154 145">{{citation|first=Monika|last=Mehta|title=Globalizing Bombay Cinema: Reproducing the Indian State and Family|journal=Cultural Dynamics|year=2005|volume=17|pages=135–154 [145]|doi=10.1177/0921374005058583|issue=2|s2cid=143950404}}</ref><ref name="Boltin 52–5">{{citation|last=Boltin|first=Kylie|title=Saathiya: South Asian Cinema Otherwise Known as 'Bollywood'|journal=[[Metro (magazine)|Metro Magazine: Media & Education Magazine]]|issue=136|date=Autumn 2003|issn=0312-2654|pages=52–5}}</ref> The awards were first introduced by the [[Filmfare]] magazine of [[The Times Group]] in 1954, the same year as the [[National Film Awards]].

Abaalmarinta Filmfare ayaa inta badan lagu tilmaamaa shirkadaha filimada Hindiga oo u dhigma [[Abaalmarinta Akadeemiyada|Abaalmarinta Akademiyada]] ee Maraykanka. Ilaa bartamihii 1990-maadkii Abaalmarinta Filmfare waxay ahayd abaal-marinaha ugu sareeya iyo abaal-marinaha ugu badan ee laga helo Bollywood-ka ilaa dhowr abaal-marin oo kale ay ka soo bexeen [[Mumbai]]. Tani waxay keentay daawashada liidata ilaa 2000-meeyadii.<ref name="Mishra 9" /><ref name="Mehta 2005 135–154 145" /><ref name="Boltin 52–5" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://spicezee.zeenews.com/articles/story80738.htm|title=Filmfare Awards have lost their gleam over the years|access-date=8 March 2011|quote=The Filmfare is equivalent to the Oscars for India.|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110816141312/http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/articles/story80738.htm|archive-date=16 August 2011|df=dmy-all}}</ref>

Marka laga soo tago xaflada caanka ah, Filmfare waxa kale oo uu leeyahay noocyo kala duwanaansho ah oo loogu talagalay warshadaha kale ee filimada Hindida, sida [[Abaalmarinta Filmfare Koonfur]] ee [[Shineemada Koonfur Hindiya]], [[Abaalmarinta Filmfare Marathi]] ee [[Shineemada Marathi]], iyo [[Abaalmarinta Filmfare Bariga]] ee Shineemada Bariga Hindiya.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/marathi/movies/news/filmfare-marathi-nominations-2016/articleshow/55576778.cms|title=Filmfare Marathi: Nominations are out - Times of India|website=The Times of India}}</ref>

